---
title: Honey-and-Ginger-Glazed Chicken with Snap Peas and Jasmine Rice
description: Vinegar, soy sauce, ginger, and honey combine for a ridiculously easy and incredibly flavorful sweet-and-sour glaze. It’s meant to coat the chicken, but we have a feeling you’ll be sneaking some on the rice and crispy snap peas as well.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-ginger-glazed-chicken-0e0da532.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/honey-ginger-glazed-chicken-130dabcb.pdf
servings: 2
cuisine: Asian
